  "instructions": [
    "Bring a large pot of water to a boil.",
    "Add the diced potatoes and sliced carrots to the pot and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped onions and minced garlic to the pot and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cod fillets to the pot and cook for 5 minutes or until cooked through.",
    "Stir in the black pepper and cayenne pepper.",
    "Carefully place the agave leaf in a large serving bowl.",
    "Fold the edges of the agave leaf over the stew to create a seal.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired.",
    "Discard the agave leaf after serving.",
    "Refrigerate any leftovers promptly."
  ],
